snippet.title: Cosmic Smash(Dreamcast) Gameplay
snippet.description:
Cosmic Smash is a game which combined squash sport and Breakout(Video game).
The objective is simple: destroy all bricks before time runs out.
You can use Trick smash to raise score. Some situation, you can perform different style of trick smash.
